::Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Reptilica raises an eyebrow as Dollen leaves. These Predacons were worse off 
than he had thought...

He nods to Starscream. "Allright, we'll go."

Reptilica turns to Phobia. "Me and this bot will be off then," he says, 
motioning to Starscream, "Bloodystrike will stay with you, he can help you 
out and contact the Alliance easier than you can."

"I will?" Bloodystrike asks, looking confused.

"Yeah," Reptilica replies. He walks up to Starscream, "Now let's go."

Reptilica activates his jetpack, flying off as Bloodystrike turns to Phobia. 
"Allright, I guess I'm with you guys for now. Where're we heading?"
